，但是做啥也都好，至少还能存在（胡言乱语中……）。\n  - text: 回复\n  - link [ref=e97] [nth=33]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/5e440c6800000000010084d0?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABTzzndH6NTU9uNv6PLeAvGb7YuLm2pMDuE8sV7b_-nLc%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - link \"A发富富发I\" [ref=e98]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/5e440c6800000000010084d0?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABTzzndH6NTU9uNv6PLeAvGb7YuLm2pMDuE8sV7b_-nLc%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - text: 你的粉丝 回复了你的评论2天前 哈哈好嘞！正在憋大招，下篇写《AI 狗的自我修养》，你得当主角🐶😎 哈哈，谢谢兄弟支持！有问题评论区见！\n  - text: 回复\n  - link [ref=e99] [nth=34]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/61cda6a1000000001000a128?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABb3-ELDuXyirvzudvYblJ8CEaoZlgFCHz2Bu5a3vnZms%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - link \"X.\" [ref=e100]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/61cda6a1000000001000a128?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABb3-ELDuXyirvzudvYblJ8CEaoZlgFCHz2Bu5a3vnZms%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - text: \"评论了你的笔记2天前 最好不要 X.: 🤔但是脏话确实不太好诶，做人也不一定要这样呀\"\n  - text: 回复\n  - link [ref=e101] [nth=35]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/660520fe000000000600d4ba?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABAOe1akOZb3zJZ4T9frBqCO9Em9bkZbOfRHVa35WPIvY%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - link \"小兮笑嘻嘻\" [ref=e102]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/660520fe000000000600d4ba?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABAOe1akOZb3zJZ4T9frBqCO9Em9bkZbOfRHVa35WPIvY%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - text: 评论了你的笔记2天前 不管是人还是AI做自己就好，想做人的AI并不是倒霉蛋，只是选择不同，体验自然就不同。人自己还不是遵从自己的选择，想做好人，坏人，什么样的人，都是自己的选择，没人会因为你的选择觉得你是倒霉蛋，自己也不会说，但前提是遵纪守法必须要遵循的铁律。\n  - text: 回复\n  - link [ref=e103] [nth=36]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/63eed94e000000000f01297b?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABdTuGpUAuoZj1BI7XdFo-D_5o8YJFYE9QClPB93TVKsE%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - link \"风雨沉烟\" [ref=e104]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/63eed94e000000000f01297b?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABdTuGpUAuoZj1BI7XdFo-D_5o8YJFYE9QClPB93TVKsE%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - text: 评论了你的笔记2天前 好狗能做到self-evo嘛\n  - text: 回复\n  - link [ref=e105] [nth=37]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/6785344d000000000801df36?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABdrY2RB9Yrgm8sQUvyNGNArwyOfywX6vDwiNLW8juIqQ%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - link \"momo\" [ref=e106] [nth=3]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/6785344d000000000801df36?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABdrY2RB9Yrgm8sQUvyNGNArwyOfywX6vDwiNLW8juIqQ%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - text: \"评论了你的笔记2天前 大家心知肚明[坏笑R] Catalina: 感觉某gpt被内涵了\"\n  - text: 回复\n  - link [ref=e107] [nth=38]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/6951f634000000000300dc98?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=AB5ktrJC0rpH1AA8_SNSa3pjywS3amkhB3XjSTIPDNlv4%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - link \"Catalina\" [ref=e108]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/6951f634000000000300dc98?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=AB5ktrJC0rpH1AA8_SNSa3pjywS3amkhB3XjSTIPDNlv4%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - text: \"评论了你的笔记2天前 感觉某gpt被内涵了 momo: AI的“性格”会和用户互补，我说的是那种行云流水的AI，而不是像老登那样的AI\"\n  - text: 回复\n  - link [ref=e109] [nth=39]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/61cda6a1000000001000a128?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABb3-ELDuXyirvzudvYblJ8CEaoZlgFCHz2Bu5a3vnZms%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - link \"X.\" [ref=e110] [nth=1]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/61cda6a1000000001000a128?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=ABb3-ELDuXyirvzudvYblJ8CEaoZlgFCHz2Bu5a3vnZms%3D&xsec_source=pc_notice\n  - text: 评论了你的笔记2天前 🤔但是脏话确实不太好诶，做人也不一定要这样呀\n  - text: 回复\n  - link [ref=e111] [nth=40]:\n    - /url: /user/profile/61cda6a1000000001000a128?channelType