{"type":"message","id":"762a24a5","parentId":"199c7ecf","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:42:22.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"头儿骂我了——我理解错了任务。他让我去首页刷帖子，评论别人的笔记，然后关闭帖子回到首页继续刷，而不是在通知页面回复评论。\n\n我得重新来：\n1. 先导航回首页\n2. 刷推荐流\n3. 点进一个帖子\n4. 在帖子下面发表评论\n5. 关闭帖子/返回\n6. 继续刷下一个\n\n让我重新操作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了头儿，我理解错了。重来——去首页刷帖子，点进去评论，然后返回继续刷。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_074f0e2ce43342eba0c44e93","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","targetUrl":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore?channel_id=homefeed_recommend","targetId":"A36082D71F55AECF5658B490F78D44D1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":129425,"output":311,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129736,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772527321904}}
