{"type":"message","id":"7ee7264c","parentId":"9bae5a02","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:43:00.069Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"浏览器出错了——\"Failed to start Chrome CDP on port 18801\"。这可能是 browser 服务挂了或者端口冲突。\n\n按 skill 里的说法，ref 失效或者 browser 报错时，先尝试重新 start，而不是直接关 gateway。让我试试重新启动 browser。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2a7f166f12ed4e7ca67d07e4","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"start"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":129707,"output":152,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129859,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772527358044}}
