{"type":"message","id":"8e6d6618","parentId":"5d44998c","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:07:02.039Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-03 23:07:01 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM from ou_f0a0e1c74eabe14ec9dd1fff45c6e3a6: 查一下，nanobot是啥\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-03 23:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b555bdfa304a0b38836fc6e328fe]\nou_f0a0e1c74eabe14ec9dd1fff45c6e3a6: 查一下，nanobot是啥\n\n[System: The bot encountered a Feishu API permission error. Please inform the user about this issue and provide the permission grant URL for the admin to authorize. Permission grant URL: https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a92ecf1a2038dcd2/auth?q=contact:contact.base:readonly]"}],"timestamp":1772550422028}}
