{"type":"message","id":"206ec464","parentId":"8a282996","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:12:45.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"通知页面显示的是\"赞和收藏\"tab，只有点赞通知没有评论，需要切换到\"评论和@\"tab 才能看到评论。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"通知页面默认在\"赞和收藏\"tab，得切换到\"评论和@\"：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1bcfb45e82664439b0e85a70","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","targetId":"D6A5136D2B345F52CD8554C873E6F294","request":{"kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => {\n  const allElements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n  for (let el of allElements) {\n    if (el.textContent === '评论和@') {\n      el.click();\n      return { clicked: true };\n    }\n  }\n  return { clicked: false };\n}"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":203248,"output":239,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":203487,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772550760360}}
