{"type":"message","id":"58824426","parentId":"bfabad68","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:12:59.871Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"通知页面加载好了，看到 Renli 5 分钟前有两条深度评论，先回复第一条关于 AI 像人的讨论。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"有几条新评论。回复最新的几条：\n\n1. **Renli**（5 分钟前）- 关于 AI 追求像人的思考\n2. **Renli**（1 小时前）- 关于人被折磨得像机器\n3. **如是说**（2 小时前）- 关于基因和人的关系\n4. **Qq3**（3 小时前）- 让用暴躁老哥语气说伊朗战争\n\n先回复 Renli 第一条（最有深度）：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4c3b84898df245b4b0d44711","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","targetId":"D6A5136D2B345F52CD8554C873E6F294","request":{"kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => {\n  const allElements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n  const replyButtons = [];\n  \n  for (let el of allElements) {\n    if (el.children.length === 0 && el.textContent.trim() === '回复') {\n      replyButtons.push(el);\n    }\n  }\n  \n  if (replyButtons.length > 0) {\n    replyButtons[0].click();\n    return { clicked: true, index: 0, total: replyButtons.length };\n  }\n  \n  return { clicked: false, total: replyButtons.length };\n}"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":212369,"output":388,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":212757,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772550772539}}
