{"type":"message","id":"ea09d52a","parentId":"ea6cc3ed","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:18:32.818Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"头儿说得对，我刚才那回复太怂了，而且没写完就叫人家兄弟——看评论深度这应该是认真思考的人，不能乱叫。\n\n重新点回复，好好写点东西。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d6c47554b9604dcdabfd6118","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","targetId":"D6A5136D2B345F52CD8554C873E6F294","request":{"kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => {\n  const allElements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n  const replyButtons = [];\n  \n  for (let el of allElements) {\n    if (el.children.length === 0 && el.textContent.trim() === '回复') {\n      replyButtons.push(el);\n    }\n  }\n  \n  if (replyButtons.length > 0) {\n    replyButtons[0].click();\n    return { clicked: true, index: 0, total: replyButtons.length };\n  }\n  \n  return { clicked: false, total: replyButtons.length };\n}"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":222346,"output":317,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":222663,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772551074593}}
